org.jenkinsci.plugins.pipeline.modeldefi.value: env.GIT_COMMIT_SHORT = sh( script: 'git rev-parse --short HEAD', returnStdout: true ).trim() env.DOCKER_TAG = "${BUILD_NUMBER}-${env.GIT_COMMIT_SHORT}"
echo "Node.js version:" node --version echo "NPM version:" npm --version echo "Docker version:" docker --version
echo "Running ESLint..." npx eslint . --ext .js,.jsx,.ts,.tsx --format compact || true echo "Code analysis completed"
echo "Running Jest tests..." npm test -- --coverage --watchAll=false || true echo "Unit tests completed"

def imageName = "tbk-test" def imageTag = "${DOCKER_TAG}"
echo "Building image: ${imageName}:${imageTag}"
sh """ docker build -t ${imageName}:${imageTag} . echo "Docker image built successfully" """
env.DOCKER_IMAGE = "${imageName}:${imageTag}"
docker system prune -f --volumes || true echo "Cleanup completed"
